## Anti-Patterns to Avoid
- ❌ Brittle selectors (use data-testid)
- ❌ Hard-coded waits (use proper waits)
- ❌ Tests depending on each other
- ❌ Not cleaning up test data
- ❌ Flaky tests (fix immediately)
- ❌ Missing test isolation
